693
00:29:25,740 --> 00:29:26,880
 Molim te,

694
00:29:26,880 --> 00:29:28,200
 smatre me ispričanim.

695
00:29:28,200 --> 00:29:30,180
 Dobro što su i pristojni još,

696
00:29:30,180 --> 00:29:31,460
 to je pozivno ljigao.

697
00:29:31,460 --> 00:29:32,880
 Treći reče,

698
00:29:32,880 --> 00:29:35,160
 oženio sam se,

699
00:29:35,440 --> 00:29:37,220
 zato ne mogu doći.

700
00:29:37,220 --> 00:29:39,280
 Sluga se povrati

701
00:29:39,280 --> 00:29:40,300
 te izvijesti o tome

702
00:29:40,300 --> 00:29:41,300
 svoga gospodara.

703
00:29:41,300 --> 00:29:43,580
 Na to domaćin srdit

704
00:29:43,580 --> 00:29:44,700
 reče svome sluzi,

705
00:29:44,700 --> 00:29:46,540
 idi brzo na tragove

706
00:29:46,540 --> 00:29:47,360
 i gradske ulice,

707
00:29:47,360 --> 00:29:48,820
 dovedi ovamo siromašne,

708
00:29:48,820 --> 00:29:50,300
 sakate, slijepe i hrome.

709
00:29:50,300 --> 00:29:51,800
 I sluga mu javi,

710
00:29:51,800 --> 00:29:53,100
 gospodaru,

711
00:29:53,100 --> 00:29:54,800
 učinjeno je što si zapovjedio,

712
00:29:54,800 --> 00:29:55,900
 a ima još mjesta.

713
00:29:55,900 --> 00:29:58,000
 Gospodar reče sluzi,

714
00:29:58,000 --> 00:29:59,540
 izidži na putove

715
00:29:59,540 --> 00:30:00,280
 i među ograde

716
00:30:00,280 --> 00:30:01,180
 i natjeraj svijet

717
00:30:01,180 --> 00:30:02,800
 da dođe da mi se napuni kuća.

718
00:30:02,800 --> 00:30:03,980
 Kaže vam,

719
00:30:03,980 --> 00:30:04,940
 nijedan od onih

720
00:30:04,940 --> 00:30:06,040
 koji bijah upozvani,

721
00:30:06,040 --> 00:30:08,200
 neće okusiti moje večere.

722
00:30:08,200 --> 00:30:12,780
 Večera označava,

723
00:30:12,780 --> 00:30:14,000
 vidjet ćemo kasnije

724
00:30:14,000 --> 00:30:14,740
 u ovom tekstu

725
00:30:14,740 --> 00:30:15,440
 iz Laodice,

726
00:30:15,440 --> 00:30:19,760
 jednu intimnost s Bogom.

727
00:30:19,760 --> 00:30:21,620
 Ti na večeru

728
00:30:21,620 --> 00:30:23,060
 odlaziš sa nekim

729
00:30:23,060 --> 00:30:24,580
 s kim želiš ustvariti

730
00:30:24,580 --> 00:30:25,520
 intiman odnos,

731
00:30:25,520 --> 00:30:26,620
 intiman kontakt.

732
00:30:26,620 --> 00:30:28,480
 Ručak često je poslovni,

733
00:30:28,480 --> 00:30:29,980
 a večera je često prijateljska

734
00:30:29,980 --> 00:30:31,740
 ili večera bračnog para,

735
00:30:31,740 --> 00:30:32,980
 romantična večera.

736
00:30:33,360 --> 00:30:34,660
 znači stvara se jedna intima,

737
00:30:34,660 --> 00:30:35,660
 jedno zajedništvo.

738
00:30:35,660 --> 00:30:38,360
 Ovi koji su pozvani

739
00:30:38,360 --> 00:30:39,940
 su se redom ispričani.

740
00:30:39,940 --> 00:30:40,840
 Sad ćemo vidjeti šta je

741
00:30:40,840 --> 00:30:42,680
 paradoksalno u cijeloj priči.

742
00:30:43,400 --> 00:30:46,100
 vidimo kako Bog ima razumijevanja

743
00:30:46,100 --> 00:30:47,760
 za naše staleške dužnosti.

744
00:30:47,760 --> 00:30:49,780
 Bog ima razumijevanja.

745
00:30:49,780 --> 00:30:51,680
 On zna da si se ti oženio,

746
00:30:51,680 --> 00:30:52,640
 da si kupio njivu

747
00:30:52,640 --> 00:30:53,800
 i da imaš pet jarmova.

748
00:30:53,800 --> 00:30:55,460
 Zato te ne zove na ručak.

749
00:30:55,460 --> 00:30:57,740
 Zove te na večeru.

750
00:30:57,740 --> 00:30:59,040
 Ko može, kaže,

751
00:30:59,040 --> 00:31:00,280
 ide gledat njivu.

752
00:31:00,280 --> 00:31:01,440
 Zove te na večeru.

753
00:31:01,440 --> 00:31:02,620
 Šta ćeš po noći vidjeti?

754
00:31:02,620 --> 00:31:04,620
 Šta je u Izraelu bila javna rasvjeta?

755
00:31:04,620 --> 00:31:07,440
 Šta ćeš vidjeti?

756
00:31:07,820 --> 00:31:08,540
 Kaže drugi,

757
00:31:08,540 --> 00:31:10,820
 imam pet jarmova volova,

758
00:31:10,820 --> 00:31:11,860
 idem ih okušat.

759
00:31:11,860 --> 00:31:12,880
 Di, po noći?

760
00:31:12,880 --> 00:31:14,900
 Oženio sam se,

761
00:31:14,900 --> 00:31:15,820
 pa dovedi ženu.

762
00:31:15,820 --> 00:31:16,960
 Ja svačate?

763
00:31:16,960 --> 00:31:19,120
 Oni se izmotavaju

764
00:31:19,120 --> 00:31:21,520
 i uzimaju svoja uslišanja,

765
00:31:21,520 --> 00:31:23,100
 blagoslove koje me Bog dao

766
00:31:23,100 --> 00:31:24,680
 kao argument da ne dolazi.

767
00:31:24,680 --> 00:31:28,140
 A Bog poštuje staleške dužnosti,

768
00:31:28,140 --> 00:31:29,520
 poštuje vrijeme čovjeka.

769
00:31:29,520 --> 00:31:30,820
 Zato je to na večer.

770
00:31:30,820 --> 00:31:33,580
 Zato je i susret zajednice petkom na večer.

771
00:31:33,580 --> 00:31:35,960
 Zato je i klanjanje subotom na večer.

772
00:31:35,960 --> 00:31:37,640
 Zato je i kateheza za odrasle

773
00:31:37,640 --> 00:31:38,820
 utorkom na večer.

774
00:31:38,820 --> 00:31:41,280
 Zato da se može doći.

775
00:31:41,280 --> 00:31:43,660
 A ko želi,

776
00:31:43,660 --> 00:31:44,700
 naći će način,

777
00:31:44,700 --> 00:31:45,220
 ko ne želi,

778
00:31:45,220 --> 00:31:46,080
 naći će izliku.

779
00:31:46,080 --> 00:31:47,360
 Ali vidite da Bog

780
00:31:47,360 --> 00:31:48,520
 se tome ruga

781
00:31:48,520 --> 00:31:49,260
 i to prezire.

782
00:31:49,260 --> 00:31:55,280
 I ko onda dolazi?

783
00:31:55,280 --> 00:31:57,800
 Dolazi oni koji su u potrebi.

784
00:31:57,800 --> 00:32:00,480
 Zato su ovi isto imali potrebu,

785
00:32:00,480 --> 00:32:03,620
 ali su uslišani u svojoj potrebi.

786
00:32:03,620 --> 00:32:05,040
 Izborili su se u molitvi

787
00:32:05,040 --> 00:32:07,240
 i njima Bog više ne treba.

788
00:32:08,420 --> 00:32:09,880
 E to je stav kakav većina

789
00:32:09,880 --> 00:32:11,960
 kršćana ima prema Bogu.

790
00:32:11,960 --> 00:32:13,580
 Ti si moj bankomat,

791
00:32:13,580 --> 00:32:15,160
 daj mi šta mi ide,

792
00:32:15,160 --> 00:32:17,120
 sad mi više ne trebaš.

793
00:32:17,120 --> 00:32:21,240
 I zato Bog često mora dopustiti

794
00:32:21,240 --> 00:32:22,640
 da postanemo hromi,

795
00:32:22,640 --> 00:32:24,100
 slijepi,

796
00:32:24,100 --> 00:32:25,260
 bolesni u potrebi,

797
00:32:25,260 --> 00:32:26,640
 da bi mu opet došli.

798
00:32:26,640 --> 00:32:31,800
 Često mi znaju doći

799
00:32:31,800 --> 00:32:33,660
 i kažu joj molim toliko dugo

800
00:32:33,660 --> 00:32:34,900
 za neku nakanu,

801
00:32:34,900 --> 00:32:35,860
 ne znam, ili posao,

802
00:32:35,860 --> 00:32:36,560
 ili brak.

803
00:32:36,560 --> 00:32:37,720
 Baš često,

804
00:32:37,720 --> 00:32:38,900
 za nje mi je često

805
00:32:38,900 --> 00:32:40,900
 dolazili ljudi s tim problemom.

806
00:32:41,280 --> 00:32:42,700
 Pita, kakav ti je odnos s Bogom?

807
00:32:42,700 --> 00:32:43,600
 Pa nikakav,

808
00:32:43,600 --> 00:32:44,080
 je li moliš?

809
00:32:44,080 --> 00:32:45,340
 Pa eto, molim samo za to.

810
00:32:45,340 --> 00:32:47,120
 Pa nije Bog lud da odreže

811
00:32:47,120 --> 00:32:48,000
 još jedini most,

812
00:32:48,000 --> 00:32:49,100
 da slomi jedini most

813
00:32:49,100 --> 00:32:50,120
 koji veže vas dvoje.

814
00:32:50,120 --> 00:32:51,360
 Da ti sad to da.

815
00:32:52,940 --> 00:32:54,820
 To je tako često sam vidio

816
00:32:54,820 --> 00:32:55,660
 takve primjere.

817
00:32:55,660 --> 00:32:57,500
 Sjećam se jednog kad sam bio

818
00:32:57,500 --> 00:32:59,360
 u evangelizaciji vani,

819
00:32:59,360 --> 00:33:00,860
 a Mišo je bio tu

820
00:33:00,860 --> 00:33:01,780
 i nazvao me poslije

821
00:33:01,780 --> 00:33:03,040
 jednog subotnjeg klanja

822
00:33:03,040 --> 00:33:03,460
 i kaže

823
00:33:03,460 --> 00:33:05,080
 na subotnjem klanjanju

824
00:33:05,080 --> 00:33:07,140
 su bili samo solo igrači.

825
00:33:07,140 --> 00:33:11,280
 Samo oni kojima je sad

826
00:33:11,280 --> 00:33:12,080
 jako stalo

827
00:33:12,080 --> 00:33:14,220
 da ih Bog usliši.

828
00:33:14,220 --> 00:33:16,080
 A ja se sjećam početak

829
00:33:16,080 --> 00:33:17,300
 a kažem to je moja pozicija

830
00:33:17,300 --> 00:33:18,300
 zašto mogu gledati

831
00:33:18,300 --> 00:33:19,280
 malo unazad

832
00:33:19,280 --> 00:33:21,000
 i vidjeti kako je to išlo.

833
00:33:21,000 --> 00:33:22,720
 Kad su su takvom

834
00:33:22,720 --> 00:33:23,600
 žarom,

835
00:33:23,600 --> 00:33:24,860
 kad su se pocrtavale

836
00:33:24,860 --> 00:33:25,360
 Biblije,

837
00:33:25,360 --> 00:33:26,800
 čitala svjedočanstva,

838
00:33:26,800 --> 00:33:28,120
 di ste sad?

839
00:33:28,120 --> 00:33:28,700
 Nema vas.

840
00:33:28,700 --> 00:33:31,480
 I sigurno imate

841
00:33:31,480 --> 00:33:32,100
 jako dobra

842
00:33:32,100 --> 00:33:33,420
 i pristojna opravdanja.

843
00:33:33,420 --> 00:33:34,820
 Ali to je tako i jadno.

844
00:33:34,820 --> 00:33:36,240
 Isus kaže

845
00:33:36,240 --> 00:33:36,960
 kaže vam

846
00:33:36,960 --> 00:33:37,760
 nijedan od onih

847
00:33:37,760 --> 00:33:38,680
 koji bijah upozvani

848
00:33:38,680 --> 00:33:40,480
 neće okusiti moje večere.

849
00:33:40,480 --> 00:33:46,140
 Moji roditelji su mi

850
00:33:46,140 --> 00:33:46,920
 o tom svjedočili.

851
00:33:46,920 --> 00:33:47,940
 Oni su baš

852
00:33:47,940 --> 00:33:49,140
 u to vremenu komunizma

853
00:33:49,140 --> 00:33:49,800
 kad nije bilo

854
00:33:49,800 --> 00:33:51,160
 uputno živjet vjeru

855
00:33:51,160 --> 00:33:52,120
 bili baš jaka

856
00:33:52,500 --> 00:33:53,360
 zajednica mladih

857
00:33:53,360 --> 00:33:54,880
 u župi Siget.

858
00:33:54,880 --> 00:33:56,400
 Moj tata i mama

859
00:33:56,400 --> 00:33:57,900
 konkretno kad je tek nastala,

860
00:33:57,900 --> 00:33:58,660
 još nije bilo,

861
00:33:58,660 --> 00:33:59,300
 su barake,

862
00:33:59,300 --> 00:34:00,080
 mislije su bile

863
00:34:00,080 --> 00:34:00,720
 u barakama,

864
00:34:00,720 --> 00:34:02,080
 su se tamo okupljali.

865
00:34:02,080 --> 00:34:03,540
 I u školi su imali

866
00:34:03,540 --> 00:34:04,660
 problema zbog toga.

867
00:34:04,660 --> 00:34:07,160
 Opominjali su ih često,

868
00:34:07,160 --> 00:34:08,460
 gledali su ih drugim očima.

869
00:34:08,460 --> 00:34:09,360
 Ali oni su bili

870
00:34:09,360 --> 00:34:09,880
 gorljivi.

871
00:34:10,980 --> 00:34:11,740
 vodio ih je tad,

872
00:34:11,740 --> 00:34:12,780
 tad je župnik bio

873
00:34:12,780 --> 00:34:14,100
 i odnosno vodio mlade,

874
00:34:14,100 --> 00:34:14,660
 cijelo vrijeme

875
00:34:14,660 --> 00:34:15,820
 fraje Manuel Hoško,

876
00:34:15,820 --> 00:34:17,000
 sad pokojni,

877
00:34:17,000 --> 00:34:17,780
 ja ga se sjećam

878
00:34:17,780 --> 00:34:18,520
 jer je jako često

879
00:34:18,520 --> 00:34:19,620
 bio kod nas kući

880
00:34:19,620 --> 00:34:21,140
 i stvarno jedan

881
00:34:21,140 --> 00:34:22,140
 onak predivan,

882
00:34:22,140 --> 00:34:23,560
 karizmatičan fratar

883
00:34:23,560 --> 00:34:24,820
 koji je okupio

884
00:34:24,820 --> 00:34:25,700
 tu dobru ekipu

885
00:34:25,700 --> 00:34:26,460
 i od njih su nastali

886
00:34:26,460 --> 00:34:27,160
 jako puno

887
00:34:27,160 --> 00:34:28,700
 bračnih parova isto.

888
00:34:28,700 --> 00:34:29,580
 Obitelji,

889
00:34:29,580 --> 00:34:30,440
 to su nama danas

890
00:34:30,440 --> 00:34:31,740
 neki obiteljski prijatelji,

891
00:34:31,740 --> 00:34:32,560
 kumovi koji znamo.

892
00:34:32,560 --> 00:34:34,760
 i sjećam se jednom,

893
00:34:34,760 --> 00:34:35,720
 to je bilo

894
00:34:35,720 --> 00:34:37,320
 tri, četiri godine prije

895
00:34:37,320 --> 00:34:37,820
 nego je umro,

896
00:34:37,820 --> 00:34:38,660
 znači nedavno

897
00:34:38,660 --> 00:34:39,580
 kad je došao

898
00:34:39,580 --> 00:34:40,320
 i baš se jadao

899
00:34:40,320 --> 00:34:40,900
 mom ocu.

900
00:34:40,900 --> 00:34:41,700
 Kaže,

901
00:34:41,700 --> 00:34:42,680
 evo,

902
00:34:42,680 --> 00:34:43,860
 od svih tih parova,

903
00:34:43,860 --> 00:34:44,980
 od svih,

904
00:34:44,980 --> 00:34:48,220
 samo su tri

905
00:34:48,220 --> 00:34:49,620
 ostala u braku danas.

906
00:34:49,620 --> 00:34:50,760
 Samo tri.

907
00:34:50,760 --> 00:34:53,080
 A znalo ih je biti

908
00:34:53,080 --> 00:34:54,840
 50, 60 na susretima.

909
00:34:54,840 --> 00:34:58,400
 Znači,

910
00:34:58,400 --> 00:34:59,480
 20 bračnih parova,

911
00:34:59,480 --> 00:34:59,700
 kaže,

912
00:34:59,700 --> 00:35:01,300
 samo tri su ostali u braku.

913
00:35:02,560 --> 00:35:03,200
 To mi je rekao

914
00:35:03,200 --> 00:35:03,880
 na rubu suza,

915
00:35:03,880 --> 00:35:04,660
 ja se sjećam tog,

916
00:35:04,660 --> 00:35:05,880
 baš me dotaklo to.

917
00:35:05,880 --> 00:35:09,800
 Ako ste nešto

918
00:35:09,800 --> 00:35:10,880
 izborili s Bogom,

919
00:35:10,880 --> 00:35:13,480
 nemojte postati mlaki,

920
00:35:13,480 --> 00:35:14,680
 nemojte rezati granu

921
00:35:14,680 --> 00:35:15,460
 na kojoj sjedite.

922
00:35:15,460 --> 00:35:17,120
 Bog vam je to dao.

923
00:35:17,120 --> 00:35:18,040
 Ja znam,

924
00:35:18,040 --> 00:35:19,260
 imali smo tu misiju

925
00:35:19,260 --> 00:35:20,980
 Šarbelovi prvorođenci

926
00:35:20,980 --> 00:35:21,780
 prošle godine

927
00:35:21,780 --> 00:35:23,500
 i Bog se tu jako proslavio,

928
00:35:23,500 --> 00:35:24,540
 bio je puno,

929
00:35:24,540 --> 00:35:24,880
 evo,

930
00:35:24,880 --> 00:35:26,380
 parova se okupilo

931
00:35:26,380 --> 00:35:27,100
 koji su molili

932
00:35:27,100 --> 00:35:28,120
 da im Bog da djete

933
00:35:28,120 --> 00:35:29,460
 i djeca su došla.

934
00:35:29,460 --> 00:35:31,100
 Mnogih baš nema više,

935
00:35:31,100 --> 00:35:32,200
 nema ih na popisima

936
00:35:32,200 --> 00:35:32,700
 klanjanja,

937
00:35:32,700 --> 00:35:33,840
 nema ih na susrtu.

938
00:35:33,840 --> 00:35:35,220
 Nema ih.

939
00:35:35,220 --> 00:35:41,720
 Postoje jedna istinita priča,

940
00:35:41,720 --> 00:35:42,820
 istinita priča,

941
00:35:42,820 --> 00:35:43,820
 o mi je karmeličanin,

942
00:35:43,820 --> 00:35:44,660
 jedan koji je ukrašič,

943
00:35:44,660 --> 00:35:45,120
 baš je,

944
00:35:45,120 --> 00:35:46,380
 evo,

945
00:35:46,380 --> 00:35:46,900
 to je možda jedan

946
00:35:46,900 --> 00:35:47,800
 radikalan primjer,

947
00:35:47,800 --> 00:35:49,120
 a svima nama poticanj,

948
00:35:49,120 --> 00:35:50,680
 o čovjeku koji je bio

949
00:35:50,680 --> 00:35:51,620
 član kinecke,

950
00:35:51,620 --> 00:35:52,780
 ove tajne crkve.

951
00:35:52,780 --> 00:35:54,400
 U Kini postoje dvije crkve,

952
00:35:54,400 --> 00:35:55,920
 jedna koja je poslušnik režima,

953
00:35:55,920 --> 00:35:56,980
 to ono što je naš

954
00:35:56,980 --> 00:35:57,860
 kardinal Stepinac

955
00:35:57,860 --> 00:35:58,400
 izbijego

956
00:35:58,400 --> 00:35:59,380
 i nije pristao,

957
00:35:59,380 --> 00:36:01,180
 da postoji crkva

958
00:36:01,180 --> 00:36:01,840
 koja je podržava,

959
00:36:01,840 --> 00:36:02,840
 i postoji jedna tajna

960
00:36:02,840 --> 00:36:03,900
 koja je odana na Vatikanu

961
00:36:03,900 --> 00:36:05,000
 koja je jako progonjena.

962
00:36:05,000 --> 00:36:06,920
